    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in a fantastic vehicle that's been well-cared for and is ready for many more miles! This car is in good condition, offering a smooth ride and a clean interior that shows its history of reliable maintenance. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a dependable, quality vehicle that looks great and performs even better. Come see for yourself why this well-maintained gem is such a great find!",
