    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, finished in a deep, glossy metallic paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no door dings, rock chips, or swirls. Inside, the cabin is a 'time capsule'\u2014the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the original floor mats are spotless, and the factory scent remains. Every electronic feature, from the navigation to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history with every milestone performed at the original dealership. The engine bay is detailed and the undercarriage is free of any debris or corrosion. I welcome any pre-purchase inspection to verify that this is one of the finest specimens currently on the market. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a flawless, collector-grade vehicle.",
